title: All the boys love Mandy Lane
description: Mandy Lane (Amber Heard) is an unattainable object of adolescent lust for all in her high school. A shy teen, Mandy is forced to entertain irritating advances while attending a weekend excursion with her classmates. She thinks these pathetic &#039;come-ons&#039; will be the worst of it, but she is horrifyingly mistaken. As her school mates are killed off one-by-one, it becomes clear that a secret admirer is harbouring some terrifying ulterior motives.
